title: Arris Touchstone Telephony Modem Documentation CD Version 4.1
description:
Arris Touchstone Telephony Modem Documentation CD Version 4.1



Contents of Disk:

1. AdbeRdr60_enu_full.exe : Adobe Acrobat reader version 6.0.1
2. attmusb.cat : ARRIS WHQL certified catalog file
3. attmusb.inf : ARRIS RNDIS USB Driver inf file
4. Microsoft License.txt : Microsoft Remote NDIS USB Driver licensing document
5. Readme.txt : this file
6. remove.exe : Utility to remove Microsoft Remote NDIS USB Driver
7. remove.sys : support file to remove Microsoft Remote NDIS USB Driver from Device Manager
8. rndismpk.sys : Remote NDIS Miniport for Windows 2000
9. rndismpm.sys : Remote NDIS Miniport for Windows ME
10. rndismpw.sys : Remote NDIS Miniport for Windows 98/SE
11. TM401 Users Guide.pdf : User's Guide for TM401
12. TM401AB Quick Install.pdf : Quick Install Guide for TM401A and TM401B
13. TM402 Users Guide.pdf : User's Guide for TM402
14. TM402AB Quick Install.pdf : Quick Install Guide for TM402A and TM402B
15. TM402GHP Quick Install.pdf : Quick Install Guide for TM402G TM402H and TM402P
16. usb8023k.sys : Microsoft Remote NDIS USB Driver for Windows 2000
17. usb8023m.sys : Microsoft Remote NDIS USB Driver for Windows ME
18. usb8023w.sys : Microsoft Remote NDIS USB Driver for Windows 98(SE)
